        <abstract>
            <p>Only more sensitive seedlings respond to flashing light.</p> 
<p>CD’s letter to <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> ["On vivisection", 22 Apr 1881] in every way admirable.</p> 
            <p>GJR to be Zoological Secretary of Linnean Society.</p> 
<p>Has decided on arrangement of material for his books <hi rend="italic">Animal intelligence</hi> [1882]</p>  
<p>and <hi rend="italic">Mental evolution in animals</hi> [1883].</p> 
        </abstract>
